title: PBS Frontline 2013 S32E01 Egypt in Crisis 1080p HDTV x264 AAC
description: It took 80 years to rise to power, but now, after only 12 months, the Muslim Brotherhood has been ousted by its longtime foe - the Egyptian military. In a special FRONTLINE report, Middle East Correspondents Martin Smith and Charles Sennott examine the rise and rapid fall of Egypt's Muslim Brotherhood. With unique access to the Brotherhood's leadership, FRONTLINE follows the Islamist movement as it plots its next move.
